Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.02,0:00:04.53,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}悲しみ連鎖の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.72,0:00:14.17,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}僕らの願いが届くまで…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.39,0:00:23.06,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}大事なものまた一つ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.98,0:00:27.68,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}モノクロの空へと消える
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.14,0:00:34.47,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}隠したキズ冷たく震え
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.91,0:00:38.85,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}自分の居場所を探す
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.21,0:00:46.66,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}常識に従うこの世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.74,0:00:51.38,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}どうしようもできないことを
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.23,0:00:55.58,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}壊していきたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.65,0:01:03.13,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}閉ざしたココロ叫んでいる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.02,0:01:10.58,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}悲しみ連鎖の中で僕らは
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.68,0:01:16.22,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}自分さえも見失いそうになって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.90,0:01:20.15,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}曖昧な答えはイラナイ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.25,0:01:26.66,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}確かな今　追いかけて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.02,0:00:04.53,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}在悲傷的連鎖之中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.72,0:00:14.17,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}在我們的願望實現之前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.39,0:00:23.06,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}又一件珍貴的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.98,0:00:27.68,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}消失在黑白的空中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.14,0:00:34.47,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}隱藏的傷痕在發冷顫抖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.91,0:00:38.85,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}去找尋我的容身之處吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.21,0:00:46.66,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}在這個遵循常識的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.74,0:00:51.38,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}想打破無可救藥的桎梏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.23,0:00:55.58,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}按自己的意志自由生活
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.65,0:01:03.13,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}封閉的心靈正發出吶喊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.02,0:01:10.58,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}在悲傷的連鎖之中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.68,0:01:16.22,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}我們幾乎快要迷失自我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.90,0:01:20.15,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}不需要曖昧的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.25,0:01:26.66,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}只需去追尋真切的現實
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,=======TEXT=======
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.94,0:01:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時刻不能放鬆戒備
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.96,0:01:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全軍準備出動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.97,0:01:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.82,0:01:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從范烏哲失陷後戰況不容樂觀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.14,0:01:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格雷戈爾將軍如此不堪一擊…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.25,0:01:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 但考慮到對手是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.19,0:01:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並非完全無法接受
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.05,0:01:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維爾金·鞏特爾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.62,0:01:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰線正壓向我方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.07,0:02:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更糟糕的是 失去范烏哲後
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.67,0:02:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經失去了打持久戰的資本
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.76,0:02:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是時候也該有大動作了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.55,0:02:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不著你提醒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.74,0:02:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下場戰役的部署即將完成
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.75,0:02:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必杞人憂天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.58,0:02:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時候不容你不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.87,0:02:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在待命便是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.51,0:02:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼對我也保密嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.22,0:02:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…耶格爾將軍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.85,0:02:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.66,0:02:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問件事可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.71,0:02:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們是什麼關係？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.49,0:02:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼問這個…你莫非
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.22,0:02:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.94,0:02:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼說呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.54,0:02:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詳情我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.58,0:02:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 他們的關係遠比看上去複雜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.80,0:03:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賽爾貝莉亞 我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.78,0:03:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時也是這種藍色玫瑰的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.83,0:03:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您讓我找到了自己的歸宿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.79,0:03:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久沒有這樣一起賞花了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.59,0:04:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人回想起過去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.95,0:04:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.19,0:04:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能站在這縷陽光下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.46,0:04:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能伴隨殿下身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.21,0:04:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都源自於您的慈悲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.13,0:04:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從那時 您為我斬斷枷鎖以來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.47,0:04:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.82,0:04:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的未來 只為您
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.01,0:05:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 為什麼我會…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.14,0:05:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.98,0:05:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.21,0:05:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還有點事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.20,0:05:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 一個個六神無主
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.86,0:05:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.59,0:05:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉魯高
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.69,0:05:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.66,0:05:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你確認沒事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.93,0:05:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要的話可以找我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.43,0:05:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 不過我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.46,0:06:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉讓你操心了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.81,0:06:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有會議 我得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.49,0:06:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回頭見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.22,0:06:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說自己沒事的人 往往都心事重重
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.65,0:06:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.45,0:06:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.37,0:07:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡著火了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.23,0:07:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗西婭？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.39,0:07:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.42,0:07:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想…烤點麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.72,0:07:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一副問題堆積如山的表情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.04,0:07:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法爾迪奧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.29,0:07:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 還好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.20,0:07:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託 別心不在焉的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.38,0:07:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時候害艾麗西婭受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.35,0:07:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功奪取范烏哲後 戰爭主動權正倒向我們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.50,0:07:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帝國軍失去資源供應保障後 勢必策劃短期決戰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.54,0:07:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們必須密切關注帝國軍動向 謹慎應對
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.61,0:07:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.49,0:07:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維爾金 我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.09,0:07:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.01,0:08:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鞏特爾少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.63,0:08:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.70,0:08:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切忌鬆懈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.86,0:08:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.82,0:08:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.15,0:08:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.53,0:08:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉魯高 有什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.21,0:08:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事的人是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.55,0:08:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給個面子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.42,0:08:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.29,0:08:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去了就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.68,0:08:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是塊掏心置腹的好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.73,0:08:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帳篷…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.66,0:08:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿 進去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.53,0:08:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.03,0:09:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正所謂坦誠相見
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.41,0:09:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「火箭筒中一株蘿蔔花」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.77,0:09:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「姑娘用笑顏將它栽培」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.24,0:09:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「心中深藏的…」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.96,0:09:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍隊裡竟然還準備了這種設施
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.79,0:09:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有建樹的部隊 待遇果然不同
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.26,0:09:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,補給方面也好說話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.53,0:09:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎 我們兩個人獨佔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.88,0:09:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼大不了的 洗第一缸水而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.60,0:09:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.48,0:09:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和我談什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.21,0:09:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說的來著 人生在世不如意者十之八九
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.85,0:09:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身經百戰的隊長 在那方面還是新兵嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.74,0:09:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看都看得出來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.60,0:09:58.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們進展不順利吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.87,0:10:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.00,0:10:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 你們是指誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.90,0:10:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們並不是那種…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.31,0:10:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我只要第七小隊運轉順暢就滿足了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.03,0:10:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我給你講個故事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.20,0:10:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次大戰中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.71,0:10:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個新兵 剛入伍時連東南西北都分不清
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.13,0:10:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只因為想保衛國家 所以拿起槍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.41,0:10:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加入了義勇軍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.14,0:10:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時一心就是打仗殺敵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.93,0:10:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 這個一無所有的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.78,0:10:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經過戰場上的歷練 終於也有了自己的好友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.89,0:10:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至還有了喜歡的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.47,0:11:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉魯高
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.28,0:11:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來介紹 這位是我的好友拉魯高
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.78,0:11:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位是今天開始加入義勇軍的埃莉諾·帕羅特上等兵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.67,0:11:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.53,0:11:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請…多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.39,0:11:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個從未談過戀愛的大老爺們兒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.22,0:11:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,略顯笨拙的 也開始努力嘗試
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.08,0:11:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手法是笨到家了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.78,0:11:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知該如何贏得那位姑娘的芳心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.90,0:11:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕比上戰場還辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.47,0:11:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他只因為今天和姑娘說過話了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.00,0:11:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天姑娘主動向自己打招呼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.30,0:11:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就樂不可支
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.29,0:12:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後嘛 就是約定俗成的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.02,0:12:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方也沒有太為難他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.45,0:12:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坦誠心意了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.01,0:12:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.50,0:12:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.23,0:12:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛想說出口時
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.71,0:12:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就從姑娘嘴裡得知自己的好友也喜歡她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.65,0:12:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家瀟灑 又有男人味
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.18,0:12:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個值得依靠的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.04,0:12:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰場上也好幾次救過自己
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.90,0:12:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考慮到為了姑娘 他們也更般配
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.59,0:12:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也不能…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.95,0:12:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內心當然掙扎過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.79,0:12:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是友情 還是自己的愛情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.38,0:12:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是能夠輕易說服自己的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.67,0:12:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.05,0:12:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是得出結論前 他的那位好友就戰死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.43,0:12:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過從結果看 他最後選擇了友情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.26,0:13:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時一下子發生了太多事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.43,0:13:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位姑娘沒有察覺到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.39,0:13:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算傷心 也沒必要讓大家都不幸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.11,0:13:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家明知才會這樣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.13,0:13:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃莉諾才沒那麼笨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.09,0:13:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃莉諾就是那位帕羅特上尉？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.72,0:13:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜 不許告訴任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.08,0:13:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說出去要你好看！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.74,0:13:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（沒打算說出去 全都是你在自曝…）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.77,0:13:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之那啥…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.01,0:13:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想說的是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.83,0:13:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這樣的人生不適合隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.99,0:13:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 謝謝 拉魯高
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.72,0:13:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以 請收好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.81,0:14:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.87,0:14:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.10,0:14:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…你不是要外出嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.53,0:14:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算這樣 也沒有麻煩你送我的必然性啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.29,0:14:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.46,0:14:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.45,0:14:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開個玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.96,0:14:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能麻煩送我去集市嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.89,0:14:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.38,0:14:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.50,0:14:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必然性呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.80,0:14:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然沒有必然性 這樣能省力些
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.71,0:14:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣…那走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.63,0:14:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 請多關照 拉瑪爾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.68,0:14:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.24,0:14:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才你用名字稱呼我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.77,0:14:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是心理作用 快開車吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.26,0:14:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.40,0:15:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝今天陪我來購物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.48,0:15:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…反正閒著慌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.92,0:15:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.96,0:15:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 今天真是大採購啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.11,0:15:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是買給誰的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.43,0:15:53.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近 哥哥看起來有點消沉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.55,0:15:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想給他做點好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.09,0:15:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真懂事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.99,0:15:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.75,0:16:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥是我唯一的親人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.01,0:16:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能總是為別人操心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.90,0:16:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次的事也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.72,0:16:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事 習慣了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.67,0:16:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真堅強啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.45,0:16:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻木了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.22,0:16:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算不上什麼堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.43,0:16:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 如果有朝一日
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.57,0:16:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都能對錯的事說不
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.72,0:16:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為那樣的世界就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.86,0:16:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.90,0:16:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法爾迪奧是個好人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.52,0:16:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.92,0:16:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.30,0:17:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 整天恍恍惚惚的不像我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.06,0:17:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須搞個明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.29,0:17:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.01,0:17:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維爾金
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.06,0:17:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.69,0:17:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事想找你談
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.28,0:17:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.24,0:17:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們最近不太搭調
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.29,0:17:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總感覺尷尬…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.14,0:17:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.56,0:18:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會變成這樣的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.06,0:18:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我也感覺不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.57,0:18:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.11,0:18:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的頂頭上司
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.05,0:18:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後總還要並肩作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.21,0:18:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 讓你有這種顧慮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.72,0:18:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.56,0:18:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要的不是道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.15,0:18:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想 像以前那樣聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.83,0:18:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維爾金呢 怎麼想？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.07,0:18:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.23,0:18:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想繼續這樣尷尬下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.25,0:18:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.58,0:18:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為自己被維爾金討厭了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.18,0:18:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我要討厭…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.62,0:18:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說什麼討厭 我其實…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.87,0:18:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.85,0:18:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是重要的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.76,0:19:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的…夥伴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.71,0:19:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗西婭？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.70,0:19:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 和好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.55,0:19:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.97,0:19:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣法爾迪奧也會安心的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.70,0:19:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.75,0:19:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要提法爾迪奧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.94,0:19:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他好像很擔心…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.52,0:19:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我和維爾金的問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.51,0:19:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和法爾迪奧有關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.79,0:19:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法爾迪奧向我告白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.11,0:19:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我該怎麼辦…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.78,0:19:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…法爾迪奧是個好人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.05,0:19:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是問這些
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.92,0:19:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在問維爾金的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.05,0:19:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問我這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.20,0:19:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.40,0:19:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是艾麗西婭和法爾迪奧的問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.06,0:20:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒資格插嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.54,0:20:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的這麼想嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.41,0:20:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你心甘情願這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.21,0:20:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.27,0:21:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回來啦 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.99,0:21:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久沒做了 有點失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.28,0:21:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,=======ED=======
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.87,0:21:46.11,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}悲しすぎる瞳が
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.57,0:21:52.78,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}この空を映す
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.15,0:22:01.17,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}掛ける言葉がわからずに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.45,0:22:07.02,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}ただ　星を数えた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.54,0:22:12.74,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}孤独で居る世界は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.12,0:22:19.52,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}得意なはずだと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.84,0:22:26.03,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}振りかえる日々　あぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.48,0:22:32.46,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}探していた　きみをひとり
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.67,0:22:39.10,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}もしもいま許されるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.39,0:22:45.79,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}きみのことだけ想うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.95,0:22:53.68,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}忘れたくない悲しみならば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.14,0:23:01.22,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}ただそれが　それだけが
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.56,0:23:07.42,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)\be1}そう  ひとつの願い
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.87,0:21:46.11,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}太過悲傷的眼眸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.57,0:21:52.78,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}映照出這片天空
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.15,0:22:01.17,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}不知該說什麼好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.45,0:22:07.02,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}只默默數著星星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.54,0:22:12.74,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}孤獨的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.12,0:22:19.52,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}早該習慣了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.84,0:22:26.03,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}回首往日
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.48,0:22:32.46,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}我曾獨自將你找尋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.67,0:22:39.10,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}若此刻能得到允許
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.39,0:22:45.79,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}我願心中只思念著你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.95,0:22:53.68,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}若不願忘卻這悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.14,0:23:01.22,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}僅此而已 唯有此心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.56,0:23:07.42,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)\be1}是的 那是唯一的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,=======NEXT=======
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.94,0:23:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫伊莎拉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.68,0:23:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全名就是伊莎拉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.42,0:23:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達魯庫斯人自古沒有姓氏
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.76,0:23:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我被鞏特爾家收為養女後
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.73,0:23:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一種不可思議的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.03,0:23:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥說 這就是一家人的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.39,0:23:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 戰場女武神
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.74,0:23:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第17章 精靈節的饋贈
